title: Brian Vike - The Vike Report (UFO Radio Show)
description:
The Vike Report radio show.  Brian Vike discussed UFO sightings and abductions with witnesses.  Great show that ran from 2007-2008.  Brian Vike no longer does radio appearances, but you can also hear lots more of Brian Vike in the Jeff Rense radio show archives at Jeff Rense radio show website, from Brian's many past appearances on that show.

There is also a link to Brian Vike's current website in this torrent
